subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: The Czech qualifier Petra Cetkovska upset the French Open champion Li Na in a dramatic third-set tie breaker to reach the final of the New Haven Open, the final tuneup before the United States Open, which starts Monday.
